Today our 
@SamaritansPurse
 767 took off for Venezuela loaded with an Emergency Field Hospital and life-saving supplies. The devastation in Caracas and surrounding areas is just heartbreaking. Around 50,000 people are missing after back-to-back earthquakes collapsed hundreds of buildings

